560x1440px.png", "id": "314658221614549", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_314658224947882_3855311909724896821_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=P8O-q7sju3QQ7kNvgEhhGPl&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC0b3yhFRKHObdiLxhn0jwB8Urf_jIItW_t6PU3fACoGw&oe=66FFD10D"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Screenshot-5_2560x1440px.png", "id": "1623928748388173", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569461_1623928751721506_1551295081848351591_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AqiT2FT8k_0Q7kNvgGAen4P&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBk_ctNgNh3_s9YALytMoskHWah_MkEEJVKQosu-N3BtQ&oe=66FFEB9E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-Landscape_2560x1440px.png", "id": "458376827132242", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982552_458376833798908_5317755352769288190_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=v5ObSILyaqYQ7kNvgG-n3Tt&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA7p3lwSxrw0Z39fAfmsqzJ36fgaNjPwPZK5s791fObNQ&oe=66FFE3B0"}, "display_name": "Simulador Soft Skills", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\u00a1Transforma tu potencial y destaca en tu carrera!\nDescubre el simulador dise\u00f1ado para mejorar tus \"Soft Skills\" a trav\u00e9s de varias c\u00e1psulas de formaci\u00f3n esenciales con las que podr\u00e1s:\n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Autoevaluar tus competencias transversales que te ayudar\u00e1n a adaptarte a diferentes entornos de trabajo.\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Defender un discurso ante una audiencia para mejorar tu comunicaci\u00f3n y hablar en p\u00fablico.\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Entrenar tus fortalezas en un discurso comercial.\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Tomar decisiones para desarrollar tus habilidades estrat\u00e9gicas y anal\u00edticas.\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Trabajar en equipo para fomentar la colaboraci\u00f3n y la eficiencia del grupo.\n6\ufe0f\u20e3 Prepararte para llevar a cabo con \u00e9xito una entrevista de trabajo.", "short_description": "\u00a1Impulsa tus \"Soft Skills\" con nuestro Simulador de Realidad Virtual! Ideal para profesionales que buscan mejorar sus habilidades interpersonales de forma inmersiva, interactiva y efectiva."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Softskills_Cover-Landscape-Padding.png", "id": "3682144288704654", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570314_3682144292037987_5131369632409068623_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZU0zS5WBtIQQ7kNvgF8TCGe&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBeFzFMRHETWDMBsoc_dvw_9or5zsFQwtj3GG_CC-ESzg&oe=66FFC2FA"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1994020534333698", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_1994020537667031_8688105079957652849_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ss4CjKKFjD0Q7kNvgEBuJAs&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB1NcM0MRoKlg2Kh8B8xv0PCCQGn7fLvpGQFZLq1WwqLA&oe=66FFE2C3"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1247184912914732", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1247184916248065_2567077078745571082_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1RdXibchD5cQ7kNvgEcUgrd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA3F0qlkuTPjHWYX9N-FFefeWU-crlr5ouLWC2kd89Jvg&oe=66FFF0F3"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "1187254515612530", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974888_1187254518945863_7395065576696775988_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TONrB6YQGXoQ7kNvgH8aRwH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC-FLF9uV66ZKtM0w-H5B9w5jJ06vTY71rVKP5x8FbrHA&oe=66FFE140"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1151595012723300", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982662_1151595016056633_8079137566055371486_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid